## Summary

This documentation covers the Android-Kotlin SDK for Amplitude analytics, detailing installation via Gradle/Maven (com.amplitude:analytics-android), configuration options including batching behavior, EU data residency, and autocapture features for sessions/app lifecycles/screen views/deep links/element interactions, event tracking methods (track, identify, revenue), user management (setUserId, setDeviceId, reset), plugin system for enrichment and destination plugins, and advanced features like COPPA control, advertising ID/app set ID usage, location tracking, offline mode, and multiple SDK instances.

